-h%E1%BA%A3i-kh%E1%BA%A9u/poem-30tYri3KEcHvKu6CPeghNw">Thần Phù hải khẩu - 神符海口</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Tr%C3%A3i/author-NlHfXoUXzue8FcsdIodRLQ">Nguyễn Trãi</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90o%C3%A0n-Huy%C3%AAn/Ti%E1%BB%85n-L%E1%BB%85-b%E1%BB%99-Ch%E1%BB%A7-s%E1%BB%B1-%C4%90a-S%C4%A9-L%C3%AA-%C4%91%C3%A0i-gi%E1%BA%A3-m%C3%A3n-h%E1%BB%93i-kinh/poem-CXfYZd4HdEQZUW_h84t1NQ">Tiễn Lễ bộ Chủ sự Đa Sĩ Lê đài giả mãn hồi kinh - 餞禮部主事多士黎臺假滿回京</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90o%C3%A0n-Huy%C3%AAn/author-h3EvqeQvlQUxq2sceUWWYQ">Đoàn Huyên</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nh%E1%BA%A1c-Phi/T%E1%BB%91ng-T%E1%BB%AD-Nham-Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-ti%C3%AAn-sinh-b%E1%BA%AFc-ph%E1%BA%A1t/poem-VpEkcAyaFtgQZaZjsc0VFQ">Tống Tử Nham Trương tiên sinh bắc phạt - 送紫岩張先生北伐</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nh%E1%BA%A1c-Phi/author-c3LgePu9281GzRSNKjalQA">Nhạc Phi</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ninh-T%E1%BB%91n/V%E1%BB%8Dng-H%C3%B9ng-v%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-c%E1%BB%91-%C4%91%C3%B4/poem-wIGXkCb0X2tDnrWKXmnV_w">Vọng Hùng vương cố đô - 望雄王故都</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ninh-T%E1%BB%91n/author-0zxx9ptNwfX9AYtkCUmYYQ">Ninh Tốn</a>)<br></div>	</div>
